item.title: Registration-Page
item.description: This registration form allows users to input their first name, last name, email, password, account type, profile picture, age, and a brief bio. It features a clean and user-friendly design, making it professional and easy to use.

item.title: Tic Tac Toe
item.description: Tic Tac Toe is a classic two-player game where players take turns marking X or O on a 3x3 grid. The goal is to align three symbols in a row, column, or diagonal to win!
